{
  "stem": "11722.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was-- we still had our mother's cooking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we went to bathe and clean and put out new clothes, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a way of life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I think back, that they kept us-- and sometimes on purpose-- that's one of the things that I-- I remember.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was slowly-- slowly they just-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when I think back, my-- my childhood was taken away at the time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they hoped that things would improve.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I guess [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they might have heard stories that things are taking place in other parts of the world, perhaps in Poland.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know-- news bits were trickling in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But to this day, I just don't understand how people would not believe that-- and not have known that, even by that time in 1941, '42, that families were being killed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had no-- we had no idea that that was taking place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I guess maybe my parents knew that it can be worse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were hoping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody lived by hope.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it-- we just-- we just resorted to that type of a life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we sort of lived like second-class citizens, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1942, '43, my father was taken away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the ghetto my father was taken away, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] leaving my mother home with six children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father was put into this work battalion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at a time, they had leniency because my father was a sugar diabetic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they sent them to a hospital like about 60 kilometers away from Munkacs.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
